---
import LiquidEther from '../components/LiquidEther.jsx';
import ScrollReveal from './ScrollReveal.jsx';
---

<section class="intro-section">
  <div class="intro-bg">
    <LiquidEther
      client:only="react"
      colors={[ '#5227FF', '#FF9FFC', '#B497CF' ]}
      mouseForce={20}
      cursorSize={100}
      isViscous
      viscous={30}
      iterationsViscous={32}
      iterationsPoisson={32}
      resolution={0.5}
      isBounce={false}
      autoDemo
      autoSpeed={0.5}
      autoIntensity={2.2}
      takeoverDuration={0.25}
      autoResumeDelay={3000}
      autoRampDuration={0.6}
    ></LiquidEther>
  </div>

  <div class="intro-content">
    <ScrollReveal
      client:load
      baseOpacity={0.3}
      enableBlur
      baseRotation={7}
      blurStrength={9}
    >
      Realizzo siti web e landing page per PMI con tecniche SEO per farti trovare 
      prima dei competitor, GEO per fare in modo che le intelligenze artificiali 
      come ChatGPT consigliano la tua attività, e modelli 3D e design avanzati per 
      rendere il tuo sito un'esperienza visiva unica.

    </ScrollReveal>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro-section {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .intro-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .intro-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 clamp(24px, 5vw, 96px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
</style>